    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and making sure every little detail is perfect. If you're looking for something that drives like a dream and looks brand new, you've found it! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
