    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the S54 3.2L high-revving inline-six, naturally aspirated with six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. The VANOS unit has been fully rebuilt with Beisan seals and a cryo-treated hub, while the rod bearings were proactively replaced with WPC-treated shells. The rear subframe has been reinforced with structural plates to ensure torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its OEM+ geometry with updated bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers. This is a zero-fault vehicle with verified compression numbers and a clean Blackstone oil report, representing the pinnacle of the E46 chassis.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Full service records included. Showroom quality.",
